I find myself quite a knowledgeable and clever girl, also I am  very pretty and romantic. I am keen on sports. Sports is very important to me, and I am sure that "the sound mind is in a sound body“. 
It seems to be foolish to describe imaginary image of a loved one. I am looking for normal, realistic man. For me it is very important to meet my special one. Though, I can say for sure that appearance is not everything. The inner beauty is much more important than beauty of the body. I want my man to be ambitious, educated and with good sense of humor. 

